<p class="showcode"><%= link_to "Do I have to clean the property before I leave?", "#" %></p>
<p style="display:none;">Please leave the bungalow in a clean and tidy state. The bungalow will be thoroughly cleaned by our caretaker after you leave.</p>

<p class="showcode"><%= link_to "My holiday is for two weeks can I have a mid-holiday clean? ", "#" %></p>
<p style="display:none;">Yes you can, this is provided at no extra charge.</p>

<p class="showcode"><%= link_to "When is the change-over day?", "#" %></p>
<div style="display:none;">
